{"service_name": "Unify Professional Services - Identity and Federation for the Police Service", "service_id": "6324432742121472", "company_name": "Unify", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Unify\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Unify Professional Services - Identity and Federation for the Police Service\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    This service draws on Unify\u2019s experience in providing IDAM solutions within Police services whereby applications from external providers are integrated securely into the Police Service Identity and Federation Service (IFS). This allows application providers to ensure user identities are verified, validated, and authenticated.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Solution deployed within the Police service\u2019s secure data centres\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     \u2022\tIL3 interactively accessed web application\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     \u2022\tIL3 interactively accessed on a PDA or mobile device\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     \u2022\tIL3 non-interactively accessed asynchronous stateless web service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     \u2022\tIL4 interactively accessed web application\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     \u2022\tIL4 non-interactively accessed asynchronous stateless web service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     IL4 interactively accessed on a PDA or mobile device\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Applications are integrated securely into the Police Service - IFS\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure user identities are verified, validated, and authenticated\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Solution deployed within the Police service\u2019s secure data centres\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Integrates with the Police local identity repositories\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Web application accessed via a browser\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     From a fixed or mobile device, e.g. PDA or laptop\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3950 per unit per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92546/6324432742121472-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92546/6324432742121472-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92546/6324432742121472-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https